# Project Summary [deadline 2020-10-05]

## Virtual Machine or native Azure services (App Service, Functions etc..) ?

* Cost
* Flexibility
* Vendor lock-in
* Stability
* Maintainability

#### Database

* Azure SQL
* Azure MariaDB
* Azure CosmosDB

